									<b>What are donations used for?</b> We use the donations to help with the maintainers out of pocket costs, e.g. running build servers etc.
									We also use it to purchase test equipment, e.g. Saleae logic analysers, and other items to assist consistent contributors in their efforts.
									We are exceptionally grateful for those who do donate, either their time or funds.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
